                <img src="https://placeholdit.imgix.net/~text?txtsize=33&txt=six-axis-chair&w=400&h=300"/>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body text-center">
                <p>Get flown around in a six-axis chair, make a model rocket and more</p>
